title: Los Angeles International Culture Film Festival (LAICFF)
desc: Los Angeles International Culture Film Festival (LAICFF) celebrates cultural diversity through the medium of film. We welcome outstanding filmmakers and films from any country in any language, as long as they demonstrate certain aspects of a particular culture or explore the meaning of cultural diversity. Bringing together these excellent films and presenting them to mass audiences in Los Angeles and film professionals from both Hollywood and the international community, LAICFF is dedicated to spreading the influence of both film arts and international culture.
